Package com.litmus7.rental.vehicle.service

Class VehicleService

java.lang.Object
com.litmus7.rental.vehicle.service.VehicleService
public class VehicleService extends Object
The VehicleService class provides business logic for managing vehicles in the rental system. It handles loading, adding, searching, renting, returning, and retrieving available vehicles.

Author: Joel Georgie
